<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Information email</title>
</head>
<style>
  * {
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Roboto", "Oxygen", "Ubuntu", "Cantarell", "Fira Sans", "Droid Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
  }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 18px;
    background-color: #E5E9F0;
  }
  header {
    width: 100vw;
    margin:0;
    background-color: #003399;
    color:  #FFCC00;
    padding: 1rem;
    display: flex;
  }
  #FE-logo {
    width: 10rem;
  }
  .email-content {
    margin: 0.5rem;
  }
  .after-greeting {
    width: 100vw;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-items: center;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .bottom-notice {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color:#696969;
  }

  .title {
    margin-top: auto;
    margin-bottom: auto;
    margin-left: 20px;
  }
</style>
<body>
<header>
  <!--<img src="https://wwww.forumecho.eu/assets/pictures/FE-logo.png" alt="FE-logo" id="FE-logo"><h1>Forum Echo</h1>-->
  <img
    src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/931996388617781269/1008434480282865664/FE-logo.png"
    alt="FE-logo" id="FE-logo"
  >
  <h1 class='title'>Forum Echo</h1>
</header>
<div class="email-content">
  <p>Hey {{name}}, someone reset the password of your ForumEcho account!</p>
  <div class="after-greeting">
    <h2>Please check that it was really you.</h2>

    <h3>If not, please take the measures listed below: </h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Immediately change the password of your email account</li>

      <li>If you used this password in other services, also change the passwords of those!</li>

      <li>If you can't sign in to your account, you can contact our support team via
        <a href='mailto:support@forumecho.eu'>
          <address>support@forumecho.eu</address></a> we can support you in other things too!
      </li>
    </ol>

    <p class="bottom-notice">{If you reset your password you can safely ignore this email.}</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>